org.apache.ignite.mxbean

Interface IgniteClusterMXBean


  • @MXBeanDescription(value="MBean that provides access to information about cluster ID and tag.")
public interface IgniteClusterMXBean
    MX Bean allows to access information about cluster ID and tag and change tag.
